# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID.
# Create a GA4 property at https://analytics.google.com, add a Web data stream
# for your site URL, then copy the Measurement ID (format: G-XXXXXXXXXX).
#
# Put the real value in a local .env.local file (git-ignored). Analytics only
# loads when this value is set, so local dev without it stays untracked.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
